acceptance_criteria: D1 mechanism chosen and recorded with rationale; D2 bare-core fallback + SDK programmatic-option posture chosen and recorded; audit alias yes/no recorded; S2 (pm-27mv) and S3 (pm-7dcf) unblocked or re-scoped per the decision
